                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex cert="low">aximo</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/>et Iunoni Reginae <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">et</supplied> <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>enio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>oci</ex></expan> Concordiae <lb n="4"/>b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciariorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>ermaniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uperioris</ex></expan> pro salute <lb n="5"/>sua et suorum <lb n="6"/>Petronius <lb n="7"/>Senilis <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VIII <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> X <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>Ian</abbr><ex>uarias</ex></expan> Pompeiano et P<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>eli</abbr><ex>gniano</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Im oberen Drittel der Stele rechteckiges Bildfeld, darin unter auf Säulen ruhendem Doppelbogen zwei einander zugewandte, männliche Figuren in tunica und Mantel, in ihren Linken Schriftrollen(?). Die Inschrift befindet sich darunter. Verrieben und bestoßen. Eine verlorene erste Zeile dürfte sich oberhalb des Bildfeldes befunden haben. (B): RSO; Schallmayer et al.; Mattern: kleinere Abweichungen in Lesung/Ergänzung.</p>
            </div>
